Package: whisper
Title: Determine language of website using multiple methodologies
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: person("Ben", "Weiher", email = "bweiher@pm.me",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A library that uses web-scraping, language processing, and present HTML indicators to determine what language a particular website is in. Now parallelized with furrr!
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
